Upgrade VLN SEEK from version 0.16.3 to v0.22.0

1. check solr, delayed_job are running. If not, do:

#start solr
RAILS_ENV=production rake seek:sunspot:solr:start

#start 2 delayed job processes
RAILS_ENV=production rake seek:workers:start :n => 2

#check delayed job status
RAILS_ENV=production rake seek:workers:status


2.deploy upgrade tasks

RAILS_ENV=production rake vln_seek:deploy





